---
/**
 * streaming-event-driven · streaming-event-driven-fundamentals · Figure 3 —
 * Level 5 "Event sourcing": fold events left → right to derive current state,
 * with a snapshot optimization. Copied VERBATIM from the source page; lives as
 * an .astro component for the same reason as Fig1. References the shared #arw,
 * #arwA and #arwG markers emitted by Fig1.
 */
---

<figure>
    <svg
        viewBox="0 0 600 150"
        role="img"
        aria-label="Events folded left to right produce current state; a snapshot lets you replay only events after it"
    >
        <g font-family="ui-sans-serif,system-ui,sans-serif">
            <g font-size="9" fill="#111110" text-anchor="middle">
                <rect x="10" y="40" width="92" height="26" rx="5" fill="#fff" stroke="#d8d4c8"
                ></rect><text x="56" y="57">Opened</text>
                <rect x="116" y="40" width="92" height="26" rx="5" fill="#fff" stroke="#d8d4c8"
                ></rect><text x="162" y="57">Deposited +100</text>
                <rect x="222" y="40" width="92" height="26" rx="5" fill="#fff" stroke="#d8d4c8"
                ></rect><text x="268" y="57">Deposited +50</text>
                <rect x="328" y="40" width="92" height="26" rx="5" fill="#fff" stroke="#d8d4c8"
                ></rect><text x="374" y="57">Withdrew −30</text>
            </g>
            <line x1="102" y1="53" x2="114" y2="53" stroke="#6b675f" marker-end="url(#arw)"></line>
            <line x1="208" y1="53" x2="220" y2="53" stroke="#6b675f" marker-end="url(#arw)"></line>
            <line x1="314" y1="53" x2="326" y2="53" stroke="#6b675f" marker-end="url(#arw)"></line>
            <line x1="420" y1="53" x2="448" y2="53" stroke="#2f5d3a" marker-end="url(#arwG)"></line>
            <rect x="450" y="38" width="100" height="30" rx="8" fill="#eef5ee" stroke="#2f5d3a"
            ></rect><text
                x="500"
                y="58"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="11"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#2f5d3a">fold = 120</text
            >
            <text
                x="280"
                y="22"
                text-anchor="middle"
                font-size="11"
                font-weight="700"
                fill="#7a1f12">FOLD events left → right to derive current state</text
            >
            <rect
                x="116"
                y="92"
                width="198"
                height="26"
                rx="6"
                fill="#fbfaf2"
                stroke="#7a1f12"
                stroke-dasharray="4 3"></rect>
            <text x="215" y="109" text-anchor="middle" font-size="9.5" fill="#7a1f12"
                >SNAPSHOT @ offset 50k = 95 · replay only events after it</text
            >
            <path d="M 215 92 L 215 68" stroke="#7a1f12" marker-end="url(#arwA)"></path>
        </g>
    </svg>
    <figcaption>
        No <code>balance</code> field anywhere — it's an opinion about the events. A snapshot is an optimization,
        never the source of truth.
    </figcaption>
</figure>
